Panzer::
She felt the heat increase.  She started to feel some of her internal 
circuits start to short out due to the heat. Her vision was no help. 
Instead of a thick dark fog, she saw a red and yellow fog.  She 
cursed her situation under her breath.  She fired her weapon one more 
time, then collapsed to her knees.  The heat was so intence, it was 
almost unbearable.  Smoke was starting to seep from the joints around 
her neck and shoulders.  She tried to hold on as long as she could.  
She leaned up, fired another shot, then blacked out.
